abilityDescription: Automatically causes minor chaos whenever something is too stable or boring, because this account just can't resist messing things up after a decade of experience.
attackDescription: Bombards opponents with endless layers of niche, obscure, and deadpan memes that only tech insiders pretend to get, leaving everyone else confused and annoyed.
